WEBVTT

00:00.059 --> 00:04.869
Firstly, if pizza disappeared, some people might actually start losing weight.

00:07.181 --> 00:09.657
Secondly, many people love to eat pizza,...

00:09.952 --> 00:14.329
...if pizza disappeared, many people may actually start eating more at home.

00:16.671 --> 00:19.779
Thirdly, pizza is said to have been invented in Italy.

00:20.073 --> 00:24.048
If pizza disappeared, entire country may go on strike.

00:24.715 --> 00:26.975
Fourthly, if pizza disappeared,...

00:27.141 --> 00:30.899
...pizza delivery guys will have a lot of free time on their hands.

00:32.229 --> 00:34.903
Fifthly, cheese and pizza go hand in hand.

00:35.214 --> 00:38.787
If pizza disappeared, sale of cheese may come down.

00:40.255 --> 00:46.073
Lastly, if pizza disappeared, fast food joints world over may start closing up.

